1. In a Test Suite press "Add wth tag" button;
2. Type tag2 or tag3;
3. Press OK button;
4. Make sure that the tests having either tag2 or tag3 are added;
5. In a Test Suite press "Remove All" then "Add wth tag" button;
6. Type tag1 | tag with spaces
7. Press OK button;
8. Make sure that the tests having either tag1 or "tag with spaces" are added;
